<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>John Fabian Witt, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/40/9781476765877" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>The Radical Fund: How a Band of Visionaries and a Million Dollars Upended America</em></a></strong><br />
<strong>(Simon and Schuster)</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&#8220;An important and meticulous look at the impact of a forgotten fund’s revolutionary work.&#8221;<br />
<em>–Kirkus</em></p>
