<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Reese Witherspoon and Harlan Coben, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/40/9781538774700" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Gone Before Goodbye</em></a></strong><br />
<strong>(Grand Central)</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&#8220;A tour de force thriller that delivers a killer premise and thundering plot with serious emotional punch.&#8221;<br />
